profile_positions.description:
Individually or in collaboration with team members from ADDIKT and Dod & Pony, I worked on a variety of projects and tasks from Motion Graphics, Project Management and Brand Strategy for Social Media.

Responsibilities:
- 3D Modelling, Texturing, Octane Rendering;
- 3D Product Visualisation;
- 2D Motion Design, 3D Animation, Compositing;
- Concept Development: ideation for 2D and 3D projects;
- Video Production;
- Sound Design, Sound FX;
- Client Management: in direct contact with the clients, managing their expectations and debriefing their feedback; 
- Project Management: scheduling and decision making of the main steps of the project in charge;
- Social Media Management and Brand Strategy for the studio: development of brand equity and strategic communication guidelines for the social media platforms.

